{"tid":1968880,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【英倫禁足】主人為寵物沙鼠製迷你藝術館仿畫鼠版名畫：牠們對長椅的興趣多於畫作","createTime":"2020-04-12T04:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T04:55:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7c61365ef7915c03a0823cae8815df9c152c72","tid":1968880,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:34:38.000Z","msg":"全球疫症肆虐，各國政府均勸喻、甚或施政禁止人民聚集。英國正實施禁足令，不少人靠玩電話、煲劇度日。倫敦則有一對情侶為其兩隻寵物沙鼠自製迷你藝術館，不少網民看到相片時都有感暫時一解疫情禁足的苦悶。<br />\n<br />\n居於英國倫敦的Filippo於維多利亞與阿爾伯特博物館（Victoria and Albert Museum）上班，過往只要時間許可也會跟女友Marianna逛畫廊及藝術館。現時禁足令下，家中除了兩人就是飼養的兩隻九個月大的沙鼠兄弟Pandoro及Tiramis&ugrave;，「Marianna提議自製一些公仔屋給牠們遊玩，我們第一時間就是想起畫廊。」<br />\n<br />\n迷你藝術館被起名為「The Gerbil Museum」，當中更有Marianna仿畫四幅名畫並將畫中主人翁變成沙鼠，包括達文西的《蒙娜麗莎》、維梅爾的《戴珍珠耳環的少女》、孟克的《吶喊》及克林姆的《吻》。然而Filippo笑說，沙鼠兄弟在逛此藝術館對其長椅、高腳椅及告示牌等擺設都很感興趣，惟獨對主角畫作卻不大理會。Filippo續指，暫時未有計劃製作更多不同公仔屋給沙鼠，然而會考慮為「The Gerbil Museum」進行擴展。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200409/large/1586434719_c6d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200409%2Flarge%2F1586434719_c6d5.jpg&h=e39dbf32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200409/large/1586434263_c5c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200409%2Flarge%2F1586434263_c5c9.jpg&h=57710eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200409/large/1586434263_4f2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200409%2Flarge%2F1586434263_4f2c.jpg&h=f518410d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200412/MFM6BFSMHYXDZJQVRFCFQP6SHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200412%2FMFM6BFSMHYXDZJQVRFCFQP6SHQ%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W3HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=a38fb2d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200412%2FMFM6BFSMHYXDZJQVRFCFQP6SHQ%2F&h=5afa7245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200412/MFM6BFSMHYXDZJQVRFCFQP6SHQ/</a>"},{"pid":"a08199f8fda303a3bc636ff84abbb49a4d3c2654","tid":1968880,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"老鼠記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}